        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You use your hatred of magic to lash out at a known spellcaster. Make a melee Strike against the required creature. If you hit and deal damage, the target is stupefied 1, or stupefied 2 on a critical hit, until the beginning of your next turn.",
